Dialogue: 1,0:23:23.87,0:23:26.43,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,他問我「你兒子是風流種子嗎」
Dialogue: 1,0:23:26.71,0:23:27.26,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,凱因弟
Dialogue: 1,0:23:27.35,0:23:28.01,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,凱因
Dialogue: 1,0:23:28.34,0:23:29.73,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 1,0:23:29.73,0:23:31.90,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,以後再也不會風流了
